  m_text: "Press and Hold the [Left Mouse Button] to aim where you want to fish.
    \r\n\nRelease the [Left Mouse Button] to cast out your fishing line.\r\n\t  Be
    careful not to hit the fish directly with the bobber or you will scare them off.\r\n\nAny
    fish in the zone around the bobber will come towards it.\r\n\nOnce a fish touches
    the bobber, a bar will appear.\r\n\nSimply Press the [Left Mouse Button] while
    the marker is over the green portion of the bar to catch the fish.\r"
