  m_text: 'Press and Hold the [Left Mouse Button] to begin charging up a stab.


    Release
    the [Left Mouse Button] to thrust the harpoon at the nearest thing.




    You
    can use the harpoon to knock anything stuck to the boat off back into the ocean.


    Anything
    else hit by the harpoon is knocked back and stunned for a quick moment.'
